  <span class="eyebrow reveal">Our Story</span>
  <h2 class="reveal" style="margin-bottom:20px;">About JayB Shop</h2>
  <div class="prose reveal">
    <p>JayB Shop is a Kigali-based clothing retailer built around one idea: sell clothes the way tailors and stockists have always trusted each other — in matched bundles, at a fair fixed price, with a real person on the other end of every order.</p>
    <p>Every product listed here is sold in fixed bundles, so what you see in stock is exactly what's available. When a bundle sells out, it's gone until the admin restocks it — no false promises, no overselling.</p>
    <p>We keep every order personal. Once you reserve a bundle, our team confirms it with you directly on WhatsApp before any payment is finalized, so you always know exactly what you're getting and when.</p>
  </div>

